description:
Alagoas, Brazil. March 18th 2020. The following are suspended, immediately, within the State of Alagoas, for the term
of 15 (fifteen) days: events of any kind with an audience of more than 500 (five hundred) people in open events and 100 (one hundred) people in closed events;

Extended on April 6th 2020 to April 20th 2020. UPDATE: Original was until April 3rd 2020. Now extended to April 20th 2020
